				<td colspan="2"><span>All bard damage does a certain percentage of the aggro that another class would get for the same. That being said, procs are included in that, but pure-hate weapons like the ones from Emp SSra or BoC work just fine. Sometimes BoC is just too slow-proccing to keep up with the others aggro in group unless you have a few levels of WAffinity.</span></td>
