				<td colspan="2"><span>Thanks for the responses guys.
<br />

<br />
So far we have 1 vote for overall reduced aggro (but not wth hate procs) and 1 vote for some songs being nerfed. Any other experiences or does anyone know for sure how this works?
<br />

<br />
More practically, what I would like to know is:
<br />

<br />
1. When kiting for a group, is there a better way to hold aggro than using chants ?
<br />

<br />
2. What is the best setup for holding aggro as a tanking bard? BoC in primary, CHoS in secondary (assuming we are not using no drop weaps) or is there a better way? What songs would be best to increase aggro when tanking?
<br />

<br />
Cheers,
<br />
-Sub
